OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing across eastern areas. Rain
OL,7,Fturning heavy in the west and
OL,8,Fspreading eastwards across all areas
OL,9,Fovernight. Turning increasingly windy,
OL,10,Fespecially over the hills and around
OL,11,Fthe coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FRain quickly clearing to
OL,14,Fleave a day of sunshine and frequent
OL,15,Fshowers. Showers will be heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes, with hail and thunder.
OL,17,FRemaining rather breezy. Temperatures
OL,18,Faround average once again.
